tags.name:
paper-stepper
`steps to completion in a vertical display`
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `paper-stepper`
 * @customElement paper-stepper
 * `steps to completion in a vertical display`
 * @demo demo/index.html
 */

attributes.name: progress-bar
attributes.description:
True if a progress bar is shown instead of dots.

Use a progress bar when there are many steps, or if there are
steps that need to be inserted during the process (based o
responses to earlier steps).
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * True if a progress bar is shown instead of dots.
       *
       * Use a progress bar when there are many steps, or if there are
       * steps that need to be inserted during the process (based o
       * responses to earlier steps).
       */

attributes.name: back-label
attributes.description: Text for the back button. Use this property to localize the element.

attributes.name: next-label
attributes.description: Text for the back button. Use this property to localize the element.

attributes.name: disable-previous
attributes.description: Boolean for disabling the previous button.

attributes.name: disable-next
attributes.description: Boolean for disabling the next button.
